===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[ball]] of [[fire]].
# An [[explosion]], which results in a fireball.
# {{lb|en|astronomy}} A [[meteor]] bright enough to cast shadows.
# A class of sailing [[dinghy]] with a single [[trapeze]] and a [[symmetrical]] [[spinnaker]], sailed by a crew of two.
# {{lb|en|heraldiccharge}} A [[charge]] made of a disc-shaped bomb shell, with four sets of flames, at the top, bottom and on either side.

